  07 Feb 2010; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> pcsc-perl-1.4.7.ebuild:
  Drop ~mips (#142036)

*pcsc-perl-1.4.7 (11 Jan 2009)

  11 Jan 2009; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +pcsc-perl-1.4.7.ebuild:
  New ebuild for pcsc-perl. Ebuild written by me. Very handy for setting 
  up and using the PC/SC smartcard tools that go with the daemon package.  
  Tested with a USB smartcard reader (Axalto Reflex USB v3).  The older 
  reader I tried (mentioned on several forum posts) won't work without 
  a firmware update.

